---
/**
 * About.astro — Tentang YPSMA (#tentang)
 * Two-column: images left, content right
 * 4 mission points with check icons, fade-in-up animation
 */
---

<section id="tentang" class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- ============================================================
         Section heading
         ============================================================ -->
    <div class="mb-12 text-center animate-fade-in-up md:mb-16">
      <span
        class="mb-3 inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-50 px-4 py-1.5 font-heading text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-primary-700"
      >
        Tentang Kami
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Tentang YPSMA
      </h2>
      <!-- Decorative green underline -->
      <div class="mx-auto mt-4 h-1 w-20 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================
         Two-column layout
         ============================================================ -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">

      <!-- ---- Left column: 2 placeholder image slots ---- -->
      <div class="relative grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <!-- Primary image slot -->
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-primary-50">
          <img
            src="/images/ypsma-kampus.png"
            alt="Gedung utama YPSMA di Sumba Timur — kampus pendidikan Islam yang asri dan modern"
            class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="400"
            height="300"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Secondary image slot (offset downward) -->
        <div class="relative mt-12 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-primary-50">
          <img
            src="/images/ypsma-siswa.png"
            alt="Siswa-siswi YPSMA sedang mengikuti kegiatan belajar mengajar di kelas"
            class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="400"
            height="300"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative accent bar -->
        <div
          class="absolute -right-3 top-1/2 hidden h-24 w-1 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-secondary-500 lg:block"
          aria-hidden="true"
        ></div>
      </div>

      <!-- ---- Right column: content & mission points ---- -->
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <p class="mb-4 font-heading text-lg font-medium text-primary-700">
          Pendidikan Islam Terpadu di Sumba Timur
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
          <p>
            Yayasan Pembina Sumba Membangun Asih (YPSMA) merupakan lembaga pendidikan
            Islam terpadu yang berlokasi di Sumba Timur, Nusa Tenggara Timur. Didirikan
            pada tahun 2020, YPSMA hadir sebagai jawaban atas kebutuhan masyarakat akan
            pendidikan yang mengintegrasikan kurikulum nasional dengan nilai-nilai keislaman.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dengan semangat "Membangun Asih", kami berkomitmen mencetak generasi muda
            yang cerdas, berakhlak mulia, dan siap menjadi pemimpin masa depan. YPSMA
            menyediakan lingkungan belajar yang aman, nyaman, dan kondusif bagi para
            siswa dari jenjang pendidikan dasar hingga menengah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission points with check icons -->
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-700">
            Misi Kami
          </h3>

          <ul class="space-y-3" role="list">
            <!-- 1 -->
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">Berakhlakul Karimah</span>
            </li>
            <!-- 2 -->
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">Cerdas Berkarakter</span>
            </li>
            <!-- 3 -->
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">Peduli Lingkungan</span>
            </li>
            <!-- 4 -->
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">Berwawasan Global</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a
            href="#program"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-primary-500 px-6 py-3 font-heading text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-primary-500/20 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary-600 hover:shadow-lg focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary-400"
          >
            Lihat Program Kami
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M5 12h14"/>
              <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Scroll-triggered fade-in animation (matches Hero.astro pattern) */
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
